📁 Technologies Used
🧠 Spring Boot 3+
🧾 MongoDB (via Spring Data MongoDB)
🌐 RESTful APIs
🔐 Postman (for testing endpoints)
📘 Swagger/OpenAPI (for documentation)
⚡ Ngrok (for global/local testing)

How to Run Locally
Java 17+
Maven
MongoDB (installed or running locally on localhost:27017)
(Optional) Ngrok for external API testing

MongoDB Collections
1. operator
2. traffic_light

🔐 API Endpoints 
Method	        Endpoint	                           Description
POST	  /api/operators/login	                   Operator login with ID & password
GET	/api/operators/operator/login-info/{id}	    Fetch operator ID and password
GET	/api/traffic-lights/info/{lightId}          Get location, current status, weight
PUT	/api/traffic-lights/update-status	          Update current status of light
GET	/swagger-ui/index.html	Swagger             documentation UI
